# Architecture — obm_gen_with_ai

> Variables: See `_project_config.mdc` for this project's base class names, import paths, and UI tokens.
> When copying to a new project: update `_project_config.mdc` only. All rules reference variables from that file.

## Pattern

UI and data flow in one direction:

```
Widget (extends {{SCREEN_BASE_CLASS}})
   │   initState() → {{INIT_EVENT_LISTENER}}  ← wires eventStream
   │   build()    → buildRoot() → {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<S,P>
   │
   ├── {{CONSUMER_BASE}}<S extends {{SERVICE_BASE}}, P extends {{PROVIDER_BASE}}<S>>
   │       switches on p.currentState
   │
   └── P extends {{PROVIDER_BASE}}<S>  (ChangeNotifier)
         │   - state machine driven by {{STATE_TYPE}}
         │   - dialog/toast/progress sent via eventStream
         │   - KHÔNG call Dio directly
         │
         └── S extends {{SERVICE_BASE}}
                │   - holds Dio client reference
                │   - calls Dio → returns parsed model
                │
                └── Dio  ← {{DIO_CREATE}} (interceptors already wired)
```

